title: Journal of Health and Social Behavior - Structured Variation in Parental Beliefs about Autism
description: Author Jane McLeod discusses her article, " Structured Variation in Parental Beliefs about Autism," co-authored by Lydia DiSabatino. The article is published in the March 2019 issue of the Journal of Health and Social Behavior.
